
Q Computer

Instruction Set

BASIC INSTRUCTIONS

OP	INSTRUCTION		ARGUMENTS
0	NONE
1	LOAD 			REG VALUE
2	LOAD_RAM 		REG ADDR
3	STORE			VALUE ADDR
4	STORE_REG		REG ADDR
 
8	ADD				REG REG
9	SUB				REG REG
A	MUL				REG REG
B	DIV				REG REG

10	CMP				REG REG
11	JMP				ADDR
12	JE				ADDR
13	JNE				ADDR
14	JG				ADDR
15	JGE				ADDR
16	JL				ADDR
17	JLE 			ADDR

MEMORY ADDRESSES
Important Memory Addresses are listed below.
They can be useful for program development.

All of the following memory addresses are read-only.
Nothing will happen if you write to them.

0x200	HARDWARE
0x201 	Current Key
0x202	Current Mouse Button
0x203	Current Mouse X
0x204	Current Mouse Y

0x210	Monitor Size X
0x211	Monitor Size Y



